[package]
name = "wireplumber"
version = "0.2.0"
authors = [ "arcnmx",]
build = "build.rs"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.70"
description = "WirePlumber bindings"
keywords = [ "pipewire", "wireplumber", "gobject",]
categories = [ "multimedia::audio", "api-bindings",]
documentation = "https://arcnmx.github.io/wireplumber.rs/v0.2.0/wireplumber/"
repository = "https://github.com/arcnmx/wireplumber.rs"
readme = "src/README.md"
license = "MIT"
include = [ "/src/**", "/build.rs", "/COPYING*",]

[dependencies]
libc = "0.2"
bitflags = "2"

[build-dependencies]
pkg-config = "0.3"
semver = "1.0"

[features]
default = [ "v0_5",]
lua = []
experimental = []
glib-signal = [ "dep:glib-signal",]
futures = [ "glib-signal?/futures", "dep:futures-channel",]
libspa = [ "dep:libspa",]
serde = [ "dep:serde",]
v0_5 = [ "ffi/v0_5", "v0_4_16",]
v0_4_2 = []
v0_4_3 = [ "v0_4_2",]
v0_4_5 = [ "v0_4_3",]
v0_4_6 = [ "v0_4_5",]
v0_4_8 = [ "v0_4_6",]
v0_4_10 = [ "v0_4_8",]
v0_4_11 = [ "v0_4_10",]
v0_4_12 = [ "v0_4_11",]
v0_4_15 = [ "v0_4_12",]
v0_4_16 = [ "v0_4_15",]

[workspace]
members = [ "sys", "examples",]

[package.metadata]
branches = [ "main", "dev",]

[badges.maintenance]
status = "actively-maintained"

[dependencies.glib]
version = "0.19"

[dependencies.gio]
version = "0.19"

[dependencies.pipewire-sys]
version = "0.8"

[dependencies.libspa-sys]
version = "0.8"

[dependencies.libspa]
version = "0.8"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.ffi]
version = "0.2.0"
path = "sys"
package = "wireplumber-sys"

[dependencies.futures-channel]
version = "0.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.glib-signal]
version = "0.4"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.futures-util]
version = "0.3"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "v0_5", "lua", "experimental", "glib-signal", "libspa", "futures", "serde",]
rustc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs", "--generate-link-to-definition",]

[package]
name = "wireplumber-sys"
version = "0.2.0"
edition = "2021"
build = "./generate/build.rs"
description = "WirePlumber FFI bindings"
keywords = [ "pipewire",]
categories = [ "external-ffi-bindings",]
documentation = "https://arcnmx.github.io/wireplumber.rs/v0.2.0/wireplumber_sys/"
homepage = "https://arcnmx.github.io/wireplumber.rs/"
repository = "https://github.com/arcnmx/wireplumber.rs/tree/main/sys"
readme = "src/README.md"
license = "MIT"
include = [ "/src/**", "/generate/build.rs", "/generate/build_version.rs", "/generate/src/lib.rs", "/build.rs",]

[dependencies]
libc = "0.2"

[build-dependencies]
system-deps = "6"

[dev-dependencies]
shell-words = "1.0.0"
tempfile = "3"

[features]
default = [ "v0_5",]
v0_5 = []

[dependencies.glib-sys]
version = "0.19"

[dependencies.gobject-sys]
version = "0.19"

[dependencies.gio-sys]
version = "0.19"

[dependencies.pipewire]
version = "0.8"
package = "pipewire-sys"

[dependencies.libspa]
version = "0.8"
package = "libspa-sys"

[package.metadata.system-deps.wireplumber_0_5]
name = "wireplumber-0.5"
version = "0.5"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "v0_5",]
rustc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs", "--generate-link-to-definition",]
